## raw residuals

# We observe an asymmetric pattern, with large positive (negative) residuals present mainly for small (large) fitted values.

  risultato <- c()
  
  for (elemento in category) {
    if (elemento %in% var_lm) {
      risultato <- c(risultato, elemento)
    }
  }
  
  return(risultato)
}
